OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,FWithin the last year, 78,000 people
OL,7,Fhad phones or bags snatched from them
OL,8,Fon British streets
OL,10,FPhone thefts have spiked by more than
OL,11,F150% since last year, leading the
OL,12,Fgovernment to pledge a crackdown on
OL,13,Fsoaring criminal activity.
OL,15,FIt is estimated that around 78,000
OL,16,Fpeople had phones or bags snatched
OL,17,Ffrom them on British streets between
OL,18,FMarch 2023 and March 2024.
