OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,FStatistics from the Crime Survey for
OL,7,FEngland and Wales, show this is a
OL,8,Fspike of 153% when compared to the
OL,9,Fyear prior.
OL,11,FHome Office analysis of the data shows
OL,12,Fthere were more than 200 incidents a
OL,13,Fday across England and Wales over that
OL,14,Ftime period.
OL,16,FJust 0.8% of "theft from the person"
OL,17,Fresulted in a charge, and 81.9% of
OL,18,Fpolice investigations were closed
OL,19,Fbefore a suspect was found.
