OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,FPolice intelligence shows this is
OL,7,Flikely being driven by increased
OL,8,Fdemand for second-hand smartphones,
OL,9,Fboth in the UK and abroad.
OL,11,FIn a bid to tackle this soaring
OL,12,Fcriminal activity, the Home Office
OL,13,Fsaid it would call tech companies and
OL,14,Fmanufacturers to a summit which would
OL,15,Flook at "the new innovations that
OL,16,Fcould take on the illegal market".
OL,18,FIt is understood this would build on
OL,19,Fanti-theft smartphone features some
OL,20,Ffirms have already rolled out.
