OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,FThe government is also expected to ask
OL,7,Fpolice chiefs to help tackle the
OL,8,Fissue, with Operation Opal - the
OL,9,Fnational police intelligence unit -
OL,10,Flaunching an intelligence probe to
OL,11,Fgather urgent information on the
OL,12,Fcriminals who steal mobile phones, and
OL,13,Fwhere these devices end up.
OL,15,FThis will provide a stronger picture
OL,16,Fof the stolen mobile phone market, and
OL,17,Fidentify what more needs to be done to
OL,18,Ftackle the problem, the Home Office
OL,19,Fsaid.
