OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,F"These figures are troubling and the
OL,7,Fgovernment is determined to do
OL,8,Fwhatever's necessary to protect people
OL,9,Fentitled to walk the streets without
OL,10,Fthe threat of robbery.
OL,12,FShe added: "As part of our Safer
OL,13,FStreets mission, this new government
OL,14,Fis determined to crack down on snatch
OL,15,Ftheft, knife-enabled robbery, and
OL,16,Fother crimes that make people feel
OL,17,Funsafe in our communities, and we are
OL,18,Fworking to get thousands more
OL,19,Funiformed officers into our
OL,20,Fcommunities to restore neighbourhood
OL,21,Fpolicing.
