OL,3,CPhone thefts up 150% as government
OL,4,Cpledges crackdown
OL,6,F"Phone companies must ensure that any
OL,7,Fstolen phones can be quickly, easily
OL,8,Fand permanently disabled, rather than
OL,9,Fre-registered for sale on the second-
OL,10,Fhand market, and we will be meeting
OL,11,Fthem soon to discuss what further
OL,12,Faction is required to make that happen.
OL,14,F"If we work together, government, tech
OL,15,Fcompanies and law enforcement can
OL,16,Fbreak the business model of the phone
OL,17,Fthieves and moped gangs who rely on
OL,18,Fthis trade."
